name: Business Coin
description: It's JUST business. It's ONLY business. It will only ever BE business. Are you conducting business? You're conducting business now. You're just doing business now. YOU'RE IN BUSINESS NOW, KID. Understand its strictly business, you have no recourse, no second chances, you only have business. You must do business, you must complete business, you must devote yourself to business. Opportunities come and go but business is eternal.
